			<div class="dablink">This article is about the history, development, and methods of Holocaust denial.  For criticism of Holocaust denial, see <a href="/wiki/Criticism_of_Holocaust_denial" title="Criticism of Holocaust denial">Criticism of Holocaust denial</a>.</div>
